OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FTurning
OL,6,Fvery windy through Saturday, showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks turning more persistent
OL,8,Flater. Bright but blustery on Easter
OL,9,FSunday, with scattered showers. Winds
OL,10,Feasing leaving a drier and warmer
OL,11,FEaster Monday.
